15
00:02:59,876 --> 00:03:01,668
Why did you choose him?

16
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,837
In all humility, Father,

17
00:03:04,049 --> 00:03:07,465
I chose him for the same reason
our King and the Queen

18
