eyes to pray to God

37
00:04:12,079 --> 00:04:14,405
whom do you think she sees?

38
00:04:15,126 --> 00:04:18,162
Whom do you think Goya
is using as models

39
00:04:18,338 --> 00:04:20,415
for his angels?

40
00:04:21,425 --> 00:04:22,967
Harlots!

41
00:04:23,177 --> 00:04:27,127
