79
00:06:40,658 --> 00:06:42,866
she's young, very lovely,

80
00:06:43,036 --> 00:06:45,075
and she smells of jasmine.

81
00:06:45,287 --> 00:06:47,115
- She does?
- She does.

82
00:06:47,332 --> 00:06:50,832
