your hands in the portrait?

100
00:08:17,429 --> 00:08:20,847
- I'll leave that up to you.
- No, it's up to you to decide.

101
00:08:21,060 --> 00:08:23,182
Hands are not easy to paint

102
00:08:23,354 --> 00:08:25,845
