- As always, Your Majesty
- So don't complain.

114
00:09:26,964 --> 00:09:29,002
I endeavor not to, Your Majesty.

115
00:09:29,214 --> 00:09:31,503
Is this the wild steed

116
00:09:31,677 --> 00:09:33,836
