my dear?

123
00:10:55,601 --> 00:10:56,882
Maybe...

124
00:10:58,813 --> 00:11:00,520
the vulture.

125
00:11:07,614 --> 00:11:09,571
May I stay

126
00:11:09,783 --> 00:11:12,653
