145
00:12:52,770 --> 00:12:55,641
Be vigilant, use your ears.

146
00:12:55,814 --> 00:12:56,894
People talk.

147
00:12:58,109 --> 00:13:01,314
You might hear somebody
claiming that matter

148
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:05,478
