777
01:13:11,350 --> 01:13:13,971
Please, sit down,
sit down, please.

778
01:13:23,654 --> 01:13:25,860
What happened to the child?

779
01:13:26,074 --> 01:13:28,029
I don't know.

780
01:13:28,700 --> 01:13:30,990
They took her from me

781
01:13:31,204 --> 01:13:32,484
before...

782
01:13:33,789 --> 01:13:36,413
